Doing your laundry should be as simple as online bill pay. Just set it up, and forget about it. OxiClean has made it just that easy. Our new Toss-N-Go Ball is a patented technology that is revolutionizing the way people do laundry. You’ll NEVER waste time measuring and pouring detergent again. It’s not a liquid detergent. It’s not a powder. It’s a solid ball that can be used for over 25 loads of laundry – and you NEVER have to take it out of your washing machine.
• Most important innovation in laundry since the washing machine
• Smart Technology measures the detergent for you
• High performance oxygenated cleaning power
• A unique "always on" system that’s good for up to a month of laundry
• Saves you hundreds of gallons of water annually by skipping the second rinse cycle
• Patented time-release delivery system
Your Price: FREE
Availablity: In Stock

Measuring detergent is a thing of the past. This ball is smart. And you can be one of the first people to experience this new laundry innovation. For a limited time, we’re giving the OxiClean Detergent Toss-N-Go ball away for free. Just pay for shipping and handling.
